item.title: CVE-2023-26104|2023-02-25T05:00:02.786Z -- n%2Fa -- lite-web-server
item.description: All versions of the package lite-web-server are vulnerable to Denial of Service (DoS) when an attacker sends an HTTP request and includes control characters that the decodeURI() function is unable to parse.
